## API Endpoints

### 1. Barcode Scanning

**`GET /api/products/scan/:barcode`**

- Look up barcode in `products` table.
- Fallback to Open Beauty Facts API if not found.
- Return submission prompt if still not found.

| Parameter | Type | Required |
|---|---|---|
| barcode | string | Yes |

---

### 2. Product Scoring

**`GET /api/products/:productId/score`**

- Retrieve all ingredients via `product_ingredients`.
- Calculate normalized score using scoring algorithm.
- Return overall score, rating classification, and full ingredient breakdown.

| Parameter | Type | Required |
|---|---|---|
| productId | uuid | Yes |

---

### 3. User Authentication

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/auth/signup` | POST | Register a new user |
| `/api/auth/login` | POST | Log in |
| `/api/auth/logout` | POST | Log out |

---

### 4. Saved Products

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/saved` | GET | Get all saved products for a user |
| `/api/saved` | POST | Save a product to user's account |
| `/api/saved/:productId` | DELETE | Remove a saved product |

---

### 5. Product Submission

**`POST /api/submissions`**

Submits an unknown product for review. Stored in `ProductSubmissions` with `status = pending`.

| Field | Type | Required |
|---|---|---|
| userId | uuid | Yes |
| product_name | text | Yes |
| brand | text | No |
| barcode | text | Yes |
| category | text | No |
| image_url | text | No |
| ingredients | text | No |

---

### 6. Admin Endpoints

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/admin/flagged-ingredients` | GET | Fetch all flagged ingredients and their status |
| `/api/admin/flagged-ingredients/:id` | PUT | Update a flagged ingredient's status |
| `/api/admin/submissions` | GET | Fetch all pending product submissions |
| `/api/admin/submissions/:id/approve` | POST | Approve submission → moves to `products` table |
| `/api/admin/submissions/:id/reject` | POST | Reject submission → updates status to rejected |

