## Row Level Security (RLS) Policies

> ⚠️ Several tables are currently marked **UNRESTRICTED**. RLS must be implemented before go-live.

| Table | Policy |
|---|---|
| `SavedProducts` | Users can only view/manage their own rows |
| `ProductSubmissions` | Users can only view/manage their own rows |
| `products` | Publicly readable; only admin can update/delete |
| `ingredients` | Publicly readable; only admin can update/delete |
| `scoring_rules` | Publicly readable; only admin can update/delete |
| `studies` | Publicly readable; only admin can update/delete |

